As noted, former TNA World Heavyweight Champion Drew Galloway recently revealed that his TNA contract was expiring this month. Galloway confirmed on Twitter tonight that he is parting ways with the company. "Thank you @IMPACTWRESTLING for these past two years & everything we achieved together," Galloway wrote. "I'll miss everyone & I'll see you down that long road" See Also Drew Galloway Reveals Idea For WWE Return Promo On Vince McMahon, What Triple H Once Told Him, More 
